Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:24.20,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Mizuno Sanae, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.20,0:00:27.96,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,She and Kouchi often talked \Nabout books together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:29.88,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,She was so young...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.88,0:00:31.58,Default,Reiko,0,0,0,,Hopefully her brothers will be okay.{I worry about her brothers.}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:34.60,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Oh, she had brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.60,0:00:36.43,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,One of them is Takeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.43,0:00:37.97,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,He's in my class.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.97,0:00:41.29,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Dear me, this is awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.29,0:00:44.22,Default,Tamie,0,0,0,,Didn't a girl in your class \Nrecently die in an accident, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.46,0:00:48.22,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,A funeral always \Nfollows one's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.80,0:00:53.27,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,I'm so tired of funerals... So very tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:58.23,Default,Ryouhei,0,0,0,,I'm so very tired of funerals...
