Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:03.82,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,I know how much of a shock it is to hear about Mizuno's sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:05.24,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,but it'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:09.15,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,We can get through this \Nif we all stick together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.13,0:01:34.39,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:36.99,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,She died.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.42,0:01:40.53,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Mizuno's sister died in \Nan accident yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:43.23,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.75,0:01:51.75,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnLeviBrush\c&HC9C6C2&\fs68\b0\blur0.5\pos(535,48)}Self-Study \NSketching
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.89,0:02:01.50,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,I wonder if Ms. Mikami is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:05.15,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,She might be sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:07.40,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,She didn't look too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.40,0:02:08.70,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,I hope she doesn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:11.08,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Hey, Sakakibara?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.08,0:02:12.06,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.06,0:02:18.06,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,You don't think Ms. Mikami has some\Nserious, life-threatening illness, do you?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.88,0:02:21.22,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'm sure she's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.22,0:02:22.67,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,You're probably right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.23,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Are you that worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:30.26,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Well, after what \Nhappened to Sakuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.26,0:02:32.88,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,And now with Mizuno's sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.88,0:02:34.01,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:37.15,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Do you think there's some \Nconnection between those accidents?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:39.93,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,I-I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.64,0:02:47.09,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:48.42,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,To do some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.10,Sign,Book,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax0.55\fs36\frx5\fry5\fay-0.007\blur0.7\fnKozuka Mincho Pr6N-CP H\frz28.069\pos(633,264)\c&H445D6A&}Yomiyama Prefectural Junior High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.10,Sign,Book,0,0,0,,{\an8\fax0.5\fs42\b0\fsp1\frx5\fry5\fay-0.05\blur0.7\fnKozuka Mincho Pr6N-CP H\pos(747,351)\frz27.226\c&H2D434D&}Class of 1972
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:06.07,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.07,0:03:08.40,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Of course I wouldn't \Nfind Misaki's name here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:18.96,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:21.86,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Did you find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:22.95,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:26.99,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Interesting. So she \Ngraduated back in '72.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:30.12,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Which class was she in?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:33.38,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Class 3, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.38,0:03:36.81,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Oh? Which one is your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.18,0:03:39.09,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,This one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.10,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Ritsuko...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.56,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,You know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.35,0:03:47.48,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Somewhat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:50.54,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,Ritsuko was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:56.13,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,But I heard she died. \NWhen did that happen?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:04:00.71,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,15 years ago. \NRight after having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.71,0:04:02.45,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,15 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:08.43,Default,Chibiki,0,0,0,,I see. So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:14.88,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Kouichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.09,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Mr. Kubodera asked me to \Nsend you to the faculty room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:24.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I see. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.85,0:04:30.86,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,Allow me to apologize in advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.34,0:04:34.79,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but this is for all of us.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.11,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,So, forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.78,0:04:46.41,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,You're aware that Mizuno Sanae died in an accident at the hospital yesterday, correct?{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.41,0:04:47.51,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.33,0:04:51.29,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but am I being \Nsuspected of something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:54.00,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,No, no. We know \Nit was an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.00,0:04:56.21,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,A very unfortunate accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.46,0:05:01.98,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,But we found Ms. Mizuno's \Ncell phone in that elevator.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:09.26,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,Were you speaking with her at around one o'clock yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:10.63,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes, I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:12.80,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,She was on the roof \Nat the time, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.81,0:05:16.94,Default,Police1,0,0,0,,And then she went \Ninto the elevator...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.35,0:05:19.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What caused the accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.11,Default,Police2,0,0,0,,That's what we're investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.11,0:05:26.45,Default,Police2,0,0,0,,All we know is that the sheaves holding the cables in place came loose, causing it to fall.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:30.28,Default,Police2,0,0,0,,That building is \Nseveral decades old,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:33.50,Default,Police2,0,0,0,,and it's been through numerous \Nstructural modifications.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.50,0:05:35.26,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,{\i1}At any rate, let's be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:38.22,Default,Mizuno,0,0,0,,{\i1}Especially where unusual \Naccidents are concerned.
