Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.25,0:06:06.25,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnEraserDust\fs48\frx-1\pos(768,171)\c&H625D58&}Akazawa\NIzumi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.25,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Sakakibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:10.62,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Are the police finished \Nquestioning you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.70,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.94,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:15.98,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,You're dismissed \Nfor the day, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:18.60,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Um, where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.91,0:06:23.32,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,The new female class officer \Nwas selected during homeroom.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:25.03,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,It's Akazawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:27.57,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Where did everyone go, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:32.99,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Please be sure to uphold \Nthe class rules at all times.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.63,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Do I make myself clear?
