Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.72,0:06:57.13,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Wanna walk home together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.87,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Where did everyone go \Nduring sixth period?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.91,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,We went to the meeting room to take care of some stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.08,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What sort of stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:20.62,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,You've witnessed some strange occurrences since you've come here, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:23.28,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,If you know what's going on, \Ncan you at least tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.08,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.08,0:07:31.35,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,All I can say is that something very \Nunpleasant might happen to you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.46,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.31,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,During that meeting,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:38.62,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Akazawa said we needed \Nto discuss something,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.22,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,without you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:46.74,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Even if you don't like what \Nhappens, just try to deal with it.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.74,0:07:48.98,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Remember that you're \Ndoing it for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.19,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,So, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:52.10,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,"All of us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.75,0:07:54.68,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}...but this is for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.68,0:07:55.65,Default,Izumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}So, forgive us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.39,0:07:59.28,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Is this one of those class rules?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:00.75,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:04.33,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I don't get it...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.00,0:08:13.13,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Can I ask for one favor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:14.51,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:17.63,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,I'd like a copy of the class roster.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:20.64,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,You didn't get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:24.08,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,It's just not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.62,0:08:29.23,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,I don't agree with how \NAkazawa is handling this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:33.61,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,It's not fair to force her \Nideas down our throats.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:37.36,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,There must be a lot you \Nwant to know, Sakakibara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.36,0:08:38.92,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:41.42,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,Feel free to ask me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.79,0:08:43.85,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,I'll tell you everything I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.85,0:08:46.50,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Wait, Takabayashi! \NAre you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:47.94,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.92,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Does Misaki Mei exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.25,0:08:52.78,Default,Takabayashi,0,0,0,,Misaki Mei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.09,Default,Mochizuki,0,0,0,,Takabayashi! Takabayashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:30.47,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Good morning. You're early today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.26,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnEraserDust\fay-0.21\blur0.5\c&H868784&\pos(766,261)}June 5
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:41.26,Sign,Board,0,0,0,,{\an8\fnEraserDust\fay-0.27\fs54\blur0.7\c&H646060&\pos(781,549)}(Fri.)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.80,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,That's that, then. \NAre there any other...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.22,0:09:57.19,Default,Kazami,0,0,0,,No, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.87,0:10:00.37,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Did something \Nhappen this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:11.69,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Let us pray so that Takabayashi's soul may rest in peace.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:14.87,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,There have been many \Ndepressing events as of late,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.87,0:10:17.20,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,but do not lose heart, \Nand do not give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:19.92,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,We will get through \Nall this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:24.09,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Remember to uphold the \Nclass rules at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:27.71,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Ms. Mikami is in a difficult position,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.71,0:10:30.63,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,but she has agreed to cooperate \Nto the best of her ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.63,0:10:33.56,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Does everyone understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.39,0:10:43.79,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.91,0:10:49.61,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.90,0:10:52.16,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey, Wakui?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.24,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.35,0:11:14.54,Default,Phone,0,0,0,,{\i1}The person you are \Ntrying to reach currently
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.54,0:11:17.56,Default,Phone,0,0,0,,{\i1}has their phone off or is \Nout of the service area.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:21.53,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.97,0:11:24.90,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.20,Default,Teshigawara,0,0,0,,Sorry.
