Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.56,0:11:32.82,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,"A rumor walks alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:39.28,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,We see something that is not human being expressed with human-like behaviors.{merged}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.28,0:11:42.37,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,This is known as personification.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.05,0:11:51.71,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Please note that these human-like behaviors are \Nbeing expressed by something that is not human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:58.43,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Pascal once said, "Man is but a \Nreed, but he is a thinking reed."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:12:00.91,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,This is not personification.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:02.56,Alternative,Kouichi,0,0,0,,So that's what they meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.28,0:12:03.03,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,It is a metaphor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:04.99,Default,Kubodera,0,0,0,,Does that make sense?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:47.59,Default,Kouichi,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.49,0:12:50.78,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.78,0:12:52.62,Default,Mei,0,0,0,,Your call was unexpected.
